summary:
...RAFAEL DEGENERATES TO A POST-TROPICAL REMNANT LOW... ...THIS IS THE FINAL NHC ADVISORY...
 As of 3:00 PM CST Sun Nov 10

 The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
